		BoolClass represents Bool generic type.

		See https://core.telegram.org/type/Bool for reference.

		Example:
		 g, err := e2e.DecodeBool(buf)
		 if err != nil {
		     panic(err)
		 }
		 switch v := g.(type) {
		 case *e2e.BoolFalse: // boolFalse#bc799737
		 case *e2e.BoolTrue: // boolTrue#997275b5
		 default: panic(v)
		 }
